25 2026, the Governor shall include in the annual budget bill an appropriation of $150,000
26 for the Program.
27 (B) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2027 AND EACH FISCAL YEAR THEREAFTER, THE
28 GOVERNOR SHALL INCLUDE IN THE ANNUAL BUDGET BILL AN APPROPRIATION OF
